'''Firas Chaouat''' ({{langx|ar|فراس شواط}}, born 8 May 1996) is a Tunisian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Club Africain]] and the [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia national team]].<ref name="Soccerway">{{Soccerway|426035|accessdate=26 January 2019}}</ref>

==Career==
In September 2022, Chaouat joined [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[Ismaily SC]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.kingfut.com/2022/09/14/ismaily-sign-tunisian-duo/|title=Ismaily sign Tunisian duo Firas Chaouat & Nour Zamen Zammouri|first=Ahmad Gamal|last=Ali|work=KingFut|date=14 September 2022|access-date=13 December 2022}}</ref>

In July 2024, he joined Tunisian side [[Étoile Sportive du Sahel|Etoile Sportive du Sahel]].

In July 2025, Chaouat joined [[Club Africain]].

